title: Sean Hayes
itunes:title: Sean Hayes
itunes:subtitle: Sean Hayes [Will & Grace, Smartless] is an actor and producer. He joins Anna to talk about his new podcast Smartless with co-host Jason Bateman and Will Arnett and the thrills of joining the podcasting world. Sean then tells Anna about his time on Broadwa
